{
  "texts": [
    "By presenting the evidence in an accessible and interactive format that included GRADE summary of findings tables, we also provided a valuable resource to the scientific community, the decision makers, the clinicians, and the general public to protect pregnant persons and their neonates even at the current stage in the pandemic.",
    "Further research, including studies with larger sample sizes from different countries and sociodemographic diversity, is required to confirm the external validity of our findings.",
    "This work underscores the significance of ongoing research and continuous vaccine safety and effectiveness monitoring, in populations at particular risk for adverse outcomes such as pregnant persons.Fig. 11Fig.",
    "1 Study flow diagram Fig. 22Fig.",
    "2 Evidence map Fig. 33Fig."
  ]
}